00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:13.760
A car drives through a road in the British&nbsp;
countryside. On its back seat, there's an&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:18.400
American woman sleeping, Greta Evans. She's woken&nbsp;
up by the driver when they finally make it to the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:22.960
house she'll be working at. The driver informs&nbsp;
her the house owners had to step out for a second&nbsp;&nbsp;

